                        <article class="box10">
                            <h3>Liquidity Providers and Market Makers</h3>

                            <p>
                                In order to provide deep liquidity and ensure transparent and continuously flowing market, <strong>alt.bet</strong>
                                will facilitate its business not only to retail bettors but also to Liquidity Providers (LPs) and
                                licensed gaming operators – Market Makers ( MMs).
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Market Makers (MMs) are trading members that act as market makers by committing to provide liquidity in
                                an instrument listed on <strong>alt.bet</strong>.
                            </p>


                            <p>
                                Market Makers (MMs)enhance <strong>alt.bet</strong> markets because they protect against variations in
                                volatility on the market,
                                guarantee transactions at all times at the best price and support the volume of transactions in the
                                Central Order Book.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Liquidity Providers (LPs) – are trading members who act on agency basis by routing customers’ orders to
                                the exchange.
                            </p>
